{"title": "Revival Addresses", "description": "\u201cSalvation begins in thinking.  People say that Christianity is blind faith; not a bit of it.  Christianity is a rational faith that comes from honest, candid, close thought. \u2026 Men often say to me, \u2018I am not a Christian, because I think for myself.\u2019  My dear friend, you are not a Christian because you don\u2019t think for yourself. You are bound not to think. You deliberately refuse to read every book that would make you think. At a meeting like this you will go out when the preaching becomes too pointed and you are compelled to think.  If I could get you men and women who are out of Christ to think for thirty consecutive minutes, I would get you saved.\u201d \r\n\r\nHere are 17 of Torrey\u2019s addresses, designed to get us to think. (Summary by MaryAnn, with excerpt from Chapter 6)", "duration": 27935, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "12529", "name": "Reuben Archer Torrey"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/revival_2505_librivox/revival_2505.jpg", "copyright_year": "1908", "genres": ["Christianity - Other"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Larry Wilson"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Introduction", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/revival_2505_librivox/revival_00_torrey_64kb.mp3", "duration": 116}, {"section": 1, "title": "God", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/revival_2505_librivox/revival_01_torrey_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1224}, {"section": 2, "title": "\"God is Love\"", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/revival_2505_librivox/revival_02_torrey_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1428}, {"section": 3, "title": "\"Found Wanting\"", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/revival_2505_librivox/revival_03_torrey_64kb.mp3", "dura